public abstract class DataAccAst
extends OperatorAst
implements Addressable

Root class for aggregated data access, i.e. take pointer or dereference, array or structure access. The operators are "&", "*", and ".". It has a base (operand(0)) and zero or more offsets. If an access sequence has indirection, e.g. a.b->c, then the indirection will be a separate operator, e.g. (StructAcc (Uop * (StructAcc . a b)) c).
